```plantuml
@startuml
participant "张三" as zhangsan
participant "李四" as lisi

alt 借钱案例
    zhangsan -> lisi : 我要借钱
    loop 循环借钱100次
        group 成功案例
            lisi --> zhangsan : 借给你
        end
        zhangsan -> lisi : 我要还钱
        lisi --> zhangsan : 收到欠款
    end
else 借钱失败
    zhangsan -> lisi : 我还要借钱
    lisi --> zhangsan : 不借了
end
@enduml
```